; in handle_relative_token with TOK_A_MONTH

2025/12/01 Dec tx
    Expenses:Food   $5.00
    Assets:Cash

2026/01/15 Jan tx
    Expenses:Food   $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2026/03/01 Mar tx
